Game lifecycle

Initialization:
Builds the board via createBoard.
Prepares name inputs via updatePlayerNameInputs.
Wires intro tabs and opens intro modal via setupIntroductionModal.
Start game:
Collects players, roles, sound toggle, then initializes UI and state via setupGame → initializePlayersUI → updateGameState.
Turn loop:
Player clicks Roll → rollDice animates → finalizeDiceRoll resolves → movePlayer animates on tiles → handleTileLanding routes to:
Corner: handleCornerTile
Challenge: handleChallengeTile
Property: handlePropertyTile
Tiles that ask questions open modal via presentQuestion, difficulty from adjustQuestionDifficulty.
On answer → checkAnswer:
Scores and ownership updates, role effects, protections, power card awarding.
End/continue:
Doubles, extra turn, or normal end resolved in endTurn, with auto-save via saveGame.
Win check each turn via checkWinCondition and summary by calculateAchievements.
Major data

Board tiles, questions, points: constant tiles in gemini.html.
Power cards: powerCardDeck, awarded by institutions and events.
Challenges: challengeDeck.
Random events: randomEvents.
Achievements: achievements.
Roles: playerRoles.
Sounds: created by createSound.
Key UI helpers

Token placement and overlap: repositionTokensOnTile.
Player score, assets, badges, power cards:
updatePlayerScore
updatePlayerAssetsUI
updatePlayerSpecialAssetsUI
Category completion bonus: checkAmendmentBonus.
Logs: logMessage.
Modals: showModal, closeModal, showInfoModal.
Power cards

Awarding with rarity: awardPowerCard.
Use flow:
Open selector: showPowerCardModal.
Apply effect: usePowerCard handles:
double_points (double next correct)
reroll (once per turn)
skip_penalty (skip rent)
shield (penalty protection)
extra_turn (after current turn)
tax_collector (collect from others)
teleport → destination UI via showTeleportOptions
steal_asset → triggers initiateAssetChallenge and resolves inside checkAnswer
Random events and achievements

Events during landings: triggerRandomEvent (e.g., all gain/lose, triple next, corner bonus).
Achievement system:
Checker: checkAchievements
Unlock + toast: unlockAchievement
Modal list: showAchievementsModal
Save/load and options

Persist/restore to localStorage: saveGame, loadGame.
Sound toggle in menu toggles the synthesized effects used by sounds via createSound.
Role selection

Build selection UI: setupRoleSelection
Store chosen roles: assignSelectedRoles
Turn outcome rules (high level)

Passing Start: +20 points (inside movePlayer).
Landing:
Unowned property: answer to own, gain points, possible penalties; institutions award power cards.
Owned by others: pay rent unless protected.
Challenge: variable points/skip-turn penalty.
Corners: special movement/bonus; doubles may grant extra move chain.
Win conditions checked in checkWinCondition:
Score ≥ 150
Own all 4 categories
All ownable tiles owned → highest score
Round limit ≥ 20 → highest score